query:
WITH entities AS (
                SELECT cf.id FROM core_credit_facilities cf
                LEFT JOIN core_collaterals co ON cf.collateral_id = co.id
                LEFT JOIN core_wallets wa ON co.wallet_id = wa.id
                WHERE wa.external_wallet_id = $1) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: CreditFacilityId", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN core_credit_facility_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.id, e.sequence
